    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a reliable daily driver with plenty of heart? This car is a fantastic choice for anyone who values a dependable engine and a smooth ride over a perfect exterior. It shows some honest signs of its years on the road, including some cosmetic wear and tear, but it has been well-maintained where it counts and is ready for many more miles. It's a solid, hardworking vehicle that\u2019s priced to move!",
