    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and some fading paint on the hood, while the interior shows significant wear on the upholstery and a few cracked trim pieces. Mechanically, the car starts and runs, but it will likely need suspension work and a brake service in the near future to ensure continued reliability. It is a solid choice for someone looking for a functional vehicle who doesn't mind putting in a little work to freshen it up.",
      "price": 19500.0,
