    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a rare opportunity to own a vehicle in truly showroom condition. This meticulously maintained masterpiece represents the pinnacle of its class, offering an uncompromising driving experience and flawless aesthetics. From the pristine interior to the mirror-finish exterior, every detail reflects a standard of care that is second to none. This is not merely a pre-owned vehicle; it is a definitive statement of quality and value for the discerning collector or enthusiast.",
      "price": 48900.0,
